Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.00,0:00:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告損傷情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.50,0:00:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特梅雷亞號中彈沈沒中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.21,0:00:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是度西斯的殘餘艦隊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.91,0:00:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，從上空出現了\N未經登記的艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.82,0:00:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特公會在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.60,0:00:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騎士精神…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.20,0:00:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.68,0:01:00.17,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.25,0:01:03.15,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.65,0:01:10.49,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說把黎明　當作是一個開始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.00,0:01:17.56,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說現在就是來臨的時刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.00,0:01:22.63,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,與你的煙雲時代交響曲\N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.71,0:01:32.24,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飛向雲海的彼端　飛往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}雲の海の向こうに　光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.55,0:01:46.92,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那一刻？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.00,0:01:54.00,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.07,0:02:01.27,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.35,0:02:11.81,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.33,0:02:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}空中先鋒艇\NLuft Vanship
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.81,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.80,0:03:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.68,0:03:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,委託筒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.99,0:03:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.73,0:04:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安斯維拉號上的組件…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳來DX信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安斯維拉號正在沈沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安斯維拉號爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格拉艾斯號脫離戰線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.87,0:04:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.11,0:04:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安斯維拉號被消滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.01,0:04:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米茲號左舷中彈\N速度降低百分之二十
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴索隆號嚴重破損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.95,0:04:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一來米納紀斯就要被攻陷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.62,0:05:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信戴芬妮大人一定會很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.17,0:05:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只安斯維拉號\N竟然連巴索隆號都無法倖免
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.89,0:05:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於度西斯違反協定的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.13,0:05:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方麥德賽艦隊遭到了\N毀滅性的打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來米納紀斯地區恐怕不保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事不宜遲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊到基爾特公會\N找不到的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.21,0:05:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，臣這就去安排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.18,0:05:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那『貨物』\N帶到世界上最安全的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.39,0:06:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把這個交給麥德賽大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼，我們快走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.96,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米茲號中彈，準備後退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是人家拜託我們\N要親手交給本人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.57,0:06:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.17,0:06:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在那礙事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.37,0:06:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我趕出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.08,0:06:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,委託筒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥德賽大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.29,0:06:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生還章只差兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就可以爬出這個地窖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.44,0:06:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和這種生活說再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.79,0:07:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯諾特號遭受砲火集中攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.46,0:07:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓連斯塔號前去救援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令，照這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.53,0:07:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方艦隊恐怕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三顆星是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.13,0:07:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有能直接交到本人手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.87,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是已經送達司令部了不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.07,0:08:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照理說先鋒艇組織\N應該要表揚我們才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.01,0:08:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至也沒拿到收訖簽名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.98,0:08:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫他們要趕我們出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這麼辦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.19,0:08:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿一個…可以證明…\N我們確實到過這艘船的…證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.16,0:08:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這東西是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.57,0:08:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.81,0:08:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要傳達\N麥德賽司令的談話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.95,0:08:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，請用心靜聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.02,0:08:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右方一點鐘方向\N發現三艘度西斯戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仰角25度，距離一哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.09,0:08:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲瞄準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.16,0:08:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方艦隊遭受來自度西斯之\N有違騎士精神的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.56,0:09:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑劣至極的暗算行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲準備發射，彈種穿甲彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.17,0:09:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離四分之三哩，敵艦散開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.94,0:09:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方艦隊絕不令騎士精神蒙羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.38,0:09:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將立志與度西斯艦隊\N對抗到最後一兵一卒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.92,0:09:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把那孩子的心意…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…好好傳達出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.73,0:09:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，把信給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.00,0:09:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才是保護麥德賽司令名譽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與榮耀的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.01,0:09:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後的…手段啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.48,0:09:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,測試測試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.51,0:09:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人過來，沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.32,0:09:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是一封致麥德賽司令的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.82,0:10:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我克勞士‧沃卡和拉薇‧海德\N斗膽在此朗讀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有人這時還自報名號的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,致親愛的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.04,0:10:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親，您什麼時候才能回來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.24,0:10:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,院子裡父親您最心愛的橄欖樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.11,0:10:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正綻放著如雲彩般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.88,0:10:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,純白而美麗的花朵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,橄欖樹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.49,0:10:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,橄欖樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.33,0:10:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說橄欖樹的白色花朵裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.37,0:10:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘊含著人們渴望和平的感情哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.07,0:10:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是聽我去世的母親說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.27,0:10:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.01,0:10:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.98,0:10:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢污辱我們司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快，繼續唸繼續唸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.18,0:10:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.79,0:11:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,院子裡父親您最心愛的橄欖樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正綻放著如雲彩般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,純白而美麗的花朵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.87,0:11:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,橄欖樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.14,0:11:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說橄欖樹的白色花朵裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.20,0:11:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘊含著人們渴望和平的感情哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.74,0:11:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平？這些傢伙想死嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.45,0:11:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等這艘船沈了，我們也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.95,0:11:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母親和管家華斯理\N為了不讓我擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，幫我唸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續唸下去，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.84,0:11:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.64,0:11:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親您…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.67,0:11:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.24,0:11:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯艦隊集合在前進路線上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發信號給殘留艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要他們別亂了隊形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.85,0:12:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母親和管家華斯理\N為了不讓我擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.12,0:12:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親您所從事的工作\N到底有多危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.52,0:12:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們都不肯告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.09,0:12:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.39,0:12:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…\N從米納紀斯逃過來的鳥群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.43,0:12:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有僕人之間流傳的謠言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻令我感覺很不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.57,0:12:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.24,0:12:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要幹什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鎮壓完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.78,0:12:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標方位025
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.78,0:12:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仰角0，距離四分之三哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.58,0:12:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯本隊於前方排開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.42,0:12:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有20艘雷帕席翁型戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.19,0:12:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，奮戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.86,0:12:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全艦突入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.43,0:12:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全艦突入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全艦突入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.87,0:13:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們唸完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.48,0:13:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.65,0:13:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.62,0:13:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓他們唸下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴族大人准你們唸了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.80,0:13:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言\N父親您所說的騎士精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.84,0:13:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些太複雜的東西我不是很懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.14,0:13:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過為了深愛橄欖花的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算在您生日時烤一個蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在諾齊亞的天空下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.29,0:13:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我祈求父親可以平安歸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.99,0:13:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荷莉‧麥德賽上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.79,0:13:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子和平民百姓\N哪會懂得什麼叫騎士精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.86,0:14:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更別說什麼先鋒艇駕駛員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是呢，我們也懂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.17,0:14:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.24,0:14:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有因為肚子餓得\N而睡不著覺過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.21,0:14:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼騎士精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.61,0:14:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是放屁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.15,0:14:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.39,0:14:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我，快開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把槍放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.98,0:14:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙方都把槍放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不分貴族和平民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.55,0:14:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論哪一方都是我重要的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.99,0:14:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同部隊的兄弟們竟然舉槍相向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.49,0:15:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為艦隊司令的我\N絕不允許這種事發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.49,0:15:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與度西斯之戰現在才剛開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.43,0:15:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有士兵都該珍惜自己的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備面對接下來的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥德賽大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.84,0:15:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位勇敢的先鋒艇駕駛員\N還在那裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.77,0:15:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，我們在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.44,0:15:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,委託筒我收到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.08,0:15:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有件工作想拜託你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.88,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.35,0:15:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請轉告我女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.89,0:15:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴她我一定會回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定傳到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.37,0:15:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酬勞怎麼算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您平安歸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.87,0:15:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酬勞下次見面時再跟您拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.06,0:16:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我挺喜歡像你們這種傻瓜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.75,0:16:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.85,0:16:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是放屁是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.42,0:16:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從米納紀斯撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.53,0:16:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射信號彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.79,0:16:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓受損的船艦往中央靠攏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.70,0:16:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我克勞索拉斯號負責殿後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.31,0:17:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥德賽艦隊回頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.05,0:17:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴索隆號即將會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.69,0:17:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉卡號在右翼待機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.36,0:17:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會被追上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.33,0:17:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方距離二分之一哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.30,0:17:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯艦隊從兩翼圍上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.47,0:17:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布里納克號，肯諾特號\N離敵方射程還剩50秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.71,0:17:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓隊形亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.94,0:17:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從前方度西斯艦隊的中央突破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.75,0:17:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...你要去哪裡啊，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.25,0:17:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去請基爾特公會他們\N制止這場戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.19,0:17:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.93,0:17:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你，阻止這場戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.67,0:18:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安那托勒的先鋒艇在請求我們\N介入戰鬥仲裁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.00,0:18:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來求救命了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.81,0:18:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.85,0:18:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種節骨眼居然不制止戰鬥\N這算哪門子公會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.69,0:18:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王八蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.89,0:18:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.22,0:18:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.12,0:18:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去做我們能做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.43,0:18:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.13,0:18:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們掉頭回來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.73,0:18:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯諾特號即將進入敵方射程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.27,0:18:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全艦準備砲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標，前方度西斯艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.04,0:18:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本艦則把火力集中在後方敵艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.58,0:18:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部砲門對準後方度西斯艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始…射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，我要使用煙霧彈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.99,0:18:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以施放多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.56,0:18:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的10秒，這是極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.56,0:18:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.51,0:19:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擋路，快讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.45,0:19:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的先鋒艇\N正在銀之戰艦的射擊線上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅色先鋒艇！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.02,0:19:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟在我後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.34,0:19:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.57,0:19:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是違反協定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦，不准出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.65,0:19:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舵轉中央
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舵轉中央
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.55,0:19:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.58,0:19:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射哪一方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.82,0:19:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.05,0:19:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是銀之戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是銀之戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.29,0:20:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.03,0:20:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.33,0:20:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標，正方位005
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.53,0:20:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俯角3度，距離二分之一哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲瞄準，彈種穿甲彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.04,0:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.61,0:20:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.92,0:20:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於銀之戰艦的奇襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯艦隊正陷於混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.92,0:20:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動力全開\N以最大航速全艦突破重圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.53,0:20:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最大航速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.91,0:20:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥德賽艦隊他們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.96,0:21:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.46,0:21:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.77,0:21:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父親怎樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.37,0:21:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心，他說他一定會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.95,0:21:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.22,0:21:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕不上參加競時賽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.13,0:21:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下只能從最後方起跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.87,0:21:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要喝水嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.69,0:22:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.99,0:22:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，好喝
